<TABLE BORDER=0 cellpadding=4 border=0 cellspacing=1 WIDTH="95%"><TR bgcolor="#D5E6E1"><TD COLSPAN=2><CENTER><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="#000080" FACE="Verdana, Arial">T O P I C  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R E V I E W</font></CENTER></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Noren</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I ran to FGs last night to see if Rage was up and/or uncamped only to find another group clearing FGs.  I started talking to them and they told me FGs still had to be cleared because they will kill Rage when he pops.  This doesn't sound right to me so I though I would ask about it here.  I mean, aren't FGs and Rage buddy buddy? They both like fire afterall  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/wink.gif">.  Can anyone confirm or deny this first hand?<P>Noren Lifespring<BR>55th Templar<BR>Keepers of Fortitude<BR>Saryrn Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hakadek - Veeshan</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">There was a full spawn of FG's when my Ragefire appeared. I didn't experiment with pulling a FG to him to see what happens but they certainly didn't rush out of the Throne room to get him  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>You really don't need to clear FG's to camp this spot, or to get to the camp either.<P>Hakadek</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Naemie</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hello  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>Just curious, can you camp RF without aggroing the FG ?</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Reto-VZ</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I had to bind at the ragefire spot because of so many pkers on my server and I got firegiants agroed on me a lot and they camped my bind spot, and I still haven't gotten ragefire! Geez 4 days now this is riduclous</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hakadek - Veeshan</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Yes, you can camp without agroing the FG's, but you do have to be careful.<P>Once you are on the ledge where Ragefire spawns you'll see that at the far point from his spawn there is a slight overhag where you have to duck, that spot is pretty safe.<P>Danger times are when the FG's are spawning, and when they are being pulled.<P>*Don't* sit if the FG's are being pulled and watch for the wandering FG's that walk down to the front entrance, they can agro if you are sitting in the wrong spot, obviously level helps, but I just wouldn't sit for safety.<P>Hakadek</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
